text: Hi All, i am developing a use case using fabric-java-sdk and i want to enable security in fabric
So what is the procedure to make transaction through java sdk ?

Hi <@U1F1CU61Y>  currently the TCerts are not supported in Java SDK. A patch is currently under review, and will be merged as soon as the author of the patch addresses the comments raised by reviewers
you can try <https://gerrit.hyperledger.org/r/#/c/3011/> however and see if it works for you

<@U1Y2R5C9L>  can i implement this by myself ?? i just want to understand the procedure to invoke a transaction like:-

1. Get the certificate
2. Sign the certificate etc.
can you please explain me these steps ?
<@U1F1CU61Y> the above patch should give you the ability to do this
it is not yet merged, but you can try this out
